{"lemma":"جَوٌّ","slug":"جَوٌّ","root":"ج.#.#","root_slug":"ج-_-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-_-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَوّ","root":"جوو","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6608"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%8C%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"air (the apparently open space above the ground)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"weather"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"atmosphere"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"atmosphere (apparent mood)","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wide valley"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"open pasture-ground"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"interior of a house"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hall"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/d͡ʒaww/","/ʒaww/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6608","headword_ar":"جَوٌّ","root":"jw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"air:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"atmosphere;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is between the heaven,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sky, and the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"air"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"region"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the heaven,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sky, and the earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowaA='N","text_ar":"اَجْوَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY jaw~i Als~amaA='i","text_ar":"فِى جَوِّ السَّمَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xvi. 81], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the air between the heaven,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sky, and the earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the middle of the sky:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Katádeh, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the air that is remote from the earth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depressed, part of the ground;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaw~apN","text_ar":"جَوَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wide part of a valley:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb:) pl. (in the latter sense, Msb, or in the former, K, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiwaA='N","text_ar":"جِوَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowiyapN","text_ar":"اَجْوِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) It has the latter meaning in the saying of Tarafeh, [addressing a lark,]"},{"kind":"quote","text":"xalaA laki Aljaw~u fabiyDiY waA@SofiriY"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wide part of the valley has become vacant for thee; so lay thine eggs, and whistle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (AA, S.) Az says, I entered, with an Arab of the desert, a [hollow place in which water collected, termed a]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daHol","text_ar":"دَحْل"},{"kind":"text","text":", in El-Khalsà, and when we came to the water, he said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA jaw~N mina AlmaA'i laA yuwqafu","text_ar":"هٰذَا جَوٌّ مِنَ المَاءِ لَا يُوقَفُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY A^aqoSaAhu","text_ar":"عَلَى اَقْصَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is an abyss of water: one knows not the utmost extent of it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vacant, void,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desolate, place, in which is no one to cheer by his company."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 293.) ―         -b4-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a house or tent; (K;) and of anything; of the dial. of Syria; also termed ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaw~apN","text_ar":"جَوَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaw~aAniY~N","text_ar":"جَوَّانِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K; [in the CK"},{"kind":"page_break","n":479},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n","text_ar":"ن"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) in which last, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uriydu jaw~FA wayuriydu bar~FA","text_ar":"اُرِيدُ جَوًّا وَيُرِيدُ بَرًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"are augmentatives for the purpose of corroboration. (TA.) ―         -b5-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaw~apN","text_ar":"جَوَّةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I desire concealment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secrecy, and he desires publicity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"br","text_ar":"بر"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["K","Jel","S","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}